  "title": "[react-instantsearch-nextjs] relax next.js peer dependency range to support v16",
  "body": "### 🐛 Current behavior\n\ncurrently, `react-instantsearch-nextjs` does not allow next.js v16 in its peer dependency range:\n\nhttps://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/blob/7cc565086f06a9ec74155002c26596b68efc53bc/packages/react-instantsearch-nextjs/package.json#L70\n\n### 🔍 Steps to reproduce\n\nin a next.js v16 project run `pnpm add react-instantsearch-nextjs`\n\n### Live reproduction\n\nn/a\n\n### 💭 Expected behavior\n\nno peer dependency error when installing with pnpm\n\n### Package version\n\nlatest\n\n### Operating system\n\n_No response_\n\n### Browser\n\n_No response_\n\n### Code of Conduct\n\n- [x] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct",
